MESSAGE: many mods and lots of time and thought into the car. to start with on the exterior; youll see the custom hood and graphics. at night youll immediately notice the back lit door handles and the halos and eyes of the punisher emblem will draw you in. the custom paint work in the projector headlights will surely get more attention than you would realize. still room to improve; i was thinking of a satin black vinyl wrap on the roof.#once you open the door and peek inside the custom orange and gray seude interior will grab your attention. behind the wheel youll notice the custom bt gauges and interior paint work. once the sun sets and the lights go on; the orange glow from the gauges; the radio trim; hvac controls and shifter will mezmorize you.#then the fun stuff happens once you turn the key and light off 8 fire breathing tire incenerating cylinders of 426 hemi goodness. grab the custom shifter and drop it into drive and you know youre in for a good time. indy cylinders put together the 426; custom head work including bigger valves; porting; polishing stronger springs and retainers all get the gases flowing. a sttel top ring was ordered for the piston to handle spray or boost if you want this motor to exceed hellcat perfromace levels; right now the motor is close to 620hp; spray it or boost it and youll see well over 800hp. a standard 6.1 manifold sits on top of this beast. to put the power to the ground their is a 3.06 getrag rear swapped in that gets turned by a new fti 3400 stall converter.#smiles are guaranteed once the pedal is pushed and not to worry; wilwood 6 piston calipers will bring the speed back from triple digits in a blink of an eye when the srx radar/laser detector warns you of danger. the kw adjustable coilovers will help dampen the shock and prevent the car from getting squirrely when slowing down or carving corners.#other custom touches are seen underhood; with fender covers; and valve cover covers.#2 items that will need attention at one point would be new tires (or even wheels; i never did find the right set for me) and the abs light is still on after replacing the abs pump and module. the downside to this is the abs and traction control system is currently disengaged; but then again that isnt a bad thing either if you know how to drive.#im looking to get $22000 or best reasonable offer for this machine and im sure i have left some things out.  you can get this car at a steal with all these mods and then add to it to reach power levels far above any hellcat; heck you can knock on the demon door and show them some taillights too.#so to some it up:#new indy 426#ported and polished eagle heads#moroso 11 quart road racing pan#power steering cooler#upgraded transmission cooler#long tube headers#3 exhaust#new fti converter#wilwood 6 pistons calipers#upgraded sways front and rear#kw coilovers#newer trans (approx. 9000 miles from donor car)#custom hid projector lights#custom gauages#seude headliner and interior trim#matching seatbelts#srx passport radar/laser#orange led halos#loads of custom bt items#custom hood#custom graphics#the car itself though has around 38;000 miles; the engine has less than 6;000 and the transmission has less than 14;000.#in 2013 the car had 33;000 now in 2017 it has 38;000 so in 4 years it had 5;000 miles put on it.
